title: CFP NATIONAL CHAMPIONSHIP FALLOUT
description:
Wendi Nix, Tom Luginbill, and Sam Acho give their reaction on the results of the CFP National Championship. Who was the biggest performers of the game? How did the Bulldogs finally overcome the Crimson Tide? Find out on the CFB Live Podcast.
